items.caption_text:
Yesterday, Instagram announced the winners of the first-ever Rings Awards 💍
Thrilled that our #FollowMeTo project with @natalyosmann was part of this journey — we were among the 13 judges celebrating creativity around the world.

Even more exciting to share that our nominees, @twinshadban , won the Rings! 👏✨

